  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Participants must be in good health,

          -  between 18-35 years of age

          -  with no prior history of neurological diseases such as multiple sclerosis, Parkinson's
             disease, stroke with paralysis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Participants with cardiac stimulators (pace-makers) and those with metal implants in
             the skull will be excluded.

          -  Pregnant women will also be excluded.

        Participants will be required to fill out a brief health questionnaire to ensure that they
        have no conditions that would prevent brain stimulation.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
